---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - crispdigital">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="py-20 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-6">
          About <span class="text-crisp-orange">crispdigital</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Passionate about creating exceptional digital experiences that drive real business results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Mission & Vision Section -->
  <div class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
            To empower businesses with cutting-edge digital solutions that drive growth, enhance user experiences, 
            and create lasting competitive advantages in the digital marketplace.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="text-4xl text-crisp-orange mb-4">üöÄ</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-crisp-green mb-2">Transforming Ideas into Impact</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Every project is an opportunity to turn your vision into a powerful digital presence that delivers measurable results.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-6">Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
            To be the trusted digital partner that businesses turn to when they want to not just compete, 
            but lead in their industry through exceptional web and mobile experiences.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="text-4xl text-crisp-green mb-4">üéØ</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-crisp-green mb-2">Excellence in Every Detail</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We're committed to delivering solutions that exceed expectations and drive real business growth.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <div class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">What Drives Us</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The principles that guide every project and client relationship.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <div class="text-4xl text-crisp-orange mb-6">üéØ</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Results-Focused</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Every line of code, every design decision, and every feature is crafted with your business goals in mind. 
            We don't just build websites‚Äîwe build solutions that drive results.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <div class="text-4xl text-crisp-orange mb-6">ü§ù</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Collaborative Approach</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Your project is a partnership. We believe in transparent communication, regular updates, and working 
            together to ensure your vision becomes reality.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <div class="text-4xl text-crisp-orange mb-6">‚ö°</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Quality & Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We're committed to delivering high-quality solutions that not only look great but perform exceptionally. 
            Fast, secure, and scalable‚Äîthat's the crispdigital standard.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Skills Section -->
  <div class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Technical Expertise</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The technologies and tools we use to bring your ideas to life.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md text-center">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Frontend</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>React</li>
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
            <li>Astro</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md text-center">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Backend</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>Node.js</li>
            <li>Express</li>
            <li>Database Design</li>
            <li>API Development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md text-center">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">Mobile</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>React Native</li>
            <li>Cross-platform Apps</li>
            <li>App Store Deployment</li>
            <li>Native Performance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md text-center">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">CMS & Tools</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li>WordPress</li>
            <li>Git & Version Control</li>
            <li>Cloud Deployment</li>
            <li>Performance Optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <div class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">How We Work</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A proven process that ensures your project is delivered on time, on budget, and exceeds expectations.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-crisp-orange text-white w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-crisp-green mb-2">Discovery</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            We start with understanding your goals, target audience, and requirements to create a clear project roadmap.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-crisp-orange text-white w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-crisp-green mb-2">Design & Plan</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            We create wireframes, mockups, and technical specifications to ensure we're aligned before development begins.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-crisp-orange text-white w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-crisp-green mb-2">Build & Test</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Development with regular check-ins, testing across devices, and iterative improvements based on feedback.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-crisp-orange text-white w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold">4</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-crisp-green mb-2">Launch & Support</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Smooth deployment, training if needed, and ongoing support to ensure your success long after launch.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <div class="py-16 bg-crisp-green text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-90 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        We'd love to hear about your project and discuss how we can bring your digital vision to life.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-crisp-orange hover:bg-crisp-orange/90 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg transition-colors duration-200">
          Get In Touch
        </a>
        <a href="/services" class="bg-white border-2 border-white text-crisp-green hover:bg-white/10 hover:text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg transition-colors duration-200">
          View Services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
